<div id="recipedescription">
Sometimes, the simplest dishes are the best. This dish from Barbuto in NYC embraces the simplicity of a roasted chicken and potatoes by enhancing it with a salsa verde that is herbal, complex and delicious.

<div id="spacer"></div>

<div id= "recipedetails">
<div id= "time"> Time </div>
<div id= "spice"> Spice </div>
<div id= "serves"> Serves </div>
</div>

